<br>
However, on the issue of laws and abortion, I still maintain my position that you cannot legislate something like this. Sure, pass laws but people will still have abortions. They will just be &quot;illegal&quot; just like people do drugs with laws against them, people steal, kill, cross the street without a crosswalk, go over the speed limit, etc. Laws are only as good as people obey them. <br>
<br>
